<br>
As for the swapping problem, I've had it too.  I've got haste and a significant chunk of HP in my range slot.  Here's my solution.  This is what the bottom keys of my first panel of hotkeys looked like when I used bow to tag or pull:<br>
<!--EZCODE CODE START--><pre> 
-----------------
|       |       |
|disarm | range |
|       |  atk  |
-----------------
|       |       |
| disc  | range |
|       |       |
-----------------
|       | inv   |
| disc  | slot  |
|       | w/bow |
-----------------</pre><!--EZCODE CODE END--><br>
If you just have a top inventory slot with your bow in it hokeyed right below or next to hotkeyed range slot, it's really easy to hotswap.  I do pretty much the same thing now with Shissar Fangs (have the dusty pouch), but I hotkey the ammo slot instead of an inventory slot and just ctl+click a single fang off the stack in ammo for swap. <p><table cellpadding="1" border="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td bgcolor="#666666"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td bgcolor="#0F1426"><table cellpadding="0" border="0" cellspacing="5"><tr><td bgcolor="#0F1426" align=center valign=middle><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140349"><img src="http://www.strike9.com/file.aspx/path=/Grongl/fullsize/GronIcon.gif" height="51" width="51" border="0"></a></td><td bgcolor="#0F1426"><a style="line-height: 13px; color: #C0C0C0; font-size: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-family: impact,verdana,arial,helvetica;"  target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140349">Grongl</a><br><a style="line-height: 13px; color: #C0C0C0; font-size: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-family: impact,verdana,arial,helvetica;" target="new" href="http://www.army-of-grobb.com/aogcustoms.htm">Troll </a><a style="line-height: 13px; color: #C0C0C0; font-size: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-family: impact,verdana,arial,helvetica;" target="new" href="http://www.cnn.com/resources/newsmakers/world/namerica/noriega.html">Warlord</a><br><a style="line-height: 13px; color: #C0C0C0; font-size: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-family: impact,verdana,arial,helvetica;"  target="new" href="http://www.lotuscult.com/">Lotus Cult<br><a style="line-height: 13px; color: #C0C0C0; font-size: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-family: impact,verdana,arial,helvetica;"  target="new" href="http://quelliousquarters.cjb.net/">Quellious</a><br></td></tr></table></td></td></tr></table></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align