<br>
If you are ST capable, priceless bows are great and can be farmed with 2 groups (maybe doable with one, never tried it).  ST is usually only cleared when the named are up for primal, so it is usually available for priceless farming.  Of course, primal bows are even better, but significantly more rare.<br>
<br>
The bow that Doomshade drops (Bow of Doom) is also plenty good to stay equipped in range lot full time.  Granted, this one should probably go to rangers first, but if all the rangers in attendance have one, it is nice.  My guild has a couple warriors with this now due to all our rangers having one already.  (It is what I use, and I don't have any plans to ever upgrade my range slot.)<br>
