<br>
Bow of Doom. zero AC +10 stamina +50 HPs and some other nice stats. range 250<br>
<br>
Primal bow AC10 +5 stamina +50 HPs also +5 on other stats and saves and will occasional proc avatar <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  range 200<br>
<br>
<br>
Ssharean Longbow(drops from Exiled I think) AC10 I think +65 HPs +10 stamina and other stats +10 on all saves. range 225<br>
<br>
Primal Bow and Ssharean bow are tough to get, but Doomshade drops the bow of doom a significant portion of the time.<br>
<br>
<br>
If those don't help then getting a bracer of Fenin Ro that drops from Ragefire. 4 second casting time of Flamebolt. ok range and 51 point fire nuke.<br>
