I dunno, I'm OBVIOUSLY partial to using a bow. I'm an archer at heart (but I don't like playing a ranger, so I just use bows with my warrior).<br>
<br>
Anyways, for me, making arrows is fun ... and making my own bow was a blast, and using it is fun.<br>
<br>
And switching out has never been a problem.<br>
<br>
Obviously that's not for everyone.<br>
<br>
But the bio orb sounds interesting ... what is it's range? Being a monk for 50 some odd levels, I grew to hate using 45 to 60 range items to &quot;pull&quot; where in most instances I'd aggro the mob or mobs I'd need long before I got to the 60 foot range to throw my damn stars. Yet another reason I like the bow. The 250 range bow I'm using now is sooooooooo liberating.<br>
